 <!-- Login Page -->

This project is a simple login page created by using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It includes form field validations and integrates with 
an open login API. The page is responsive and works well on both web and mobile devices.

<!-- Features -->
In this i have created these things as shown in below.
--> Username/email field
--> Password field
--> Submit button
--> Client-side field validations
--> API integration for authentication
--> Responsive design
--> Show/hide password functionality
--> Remember me checkbox
--> Loading spinner during the API call


